description:
This is a 14 minute workout called '15 Min Yoga FULL BODY STRETCH & Deep Relaxation' from the channel Yoga With Bird.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is a 15 minute yoga full body stretch.
Doing this yin inspired yoga class will help to deeply stretch the entire body while releasing tension and promoting relaxation.
You can do this routine anytime of the day however it is a great addition to ones bedtime routine to help improve sleep.
This 15 min yoga stretch will also help to increase flexibility over time.
Remember to listen to the body and never do anything that causes pain or uncertain discomfort.
